Has a soft breathable seat, and you won&amp;#8217;t suffer from fatigue on a long-distance ride. The thick and sturdy 12&quot; tires absorb most shock, offering a comfortable riding experience. The 9.5&quot; wide deck provides enough room for your feet or even a small pet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
