It has a large 14&quot; electric bicycle-like wheels, which can handle even the bumpiest of roads with ease, the pneumatic tires are tough enough to handle just about any situation, and the scooter&amp;#8217;s durable one-piece wheel hubs and high-strength steel frame make it strong enough to support riders up to 265lbs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
