Equipped with detachable seat and basket, it&amp;#8217;s more convenient for you to pack and carry some daily supplies. Equipped with high-speed gear motors that can provide more power to climb 15-degree hills with ease. 450W rear-drive motor offers 22MPH top speed. The big capacity battery allows Max travel range of up to 31 miles under specific conditions, and max load of 220 lbs.The well-constrcuted and sturdy metal body and deck last longer, and the 14-inch pneumatic tires are more comfortable and durable, suitable for more terrain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
