&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9. Gigabyte BRIX:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Gigabyte&amp;#8217;s BRIX series offers mini PCs with various processor options, including Intel&amp;#8217;s 11th Gen CPUs. They are known for their compact design and versatility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;imageblock&quot;&gt;
